results.name: Number of distinct products a1*a2*...*an where 1<=ai<=n.
link: Gerhard Kirchner, Theory and aspects of extension
program: (PARI) a(n) = my(l = List()); forvec(x = vector(n, i, [1,n]), listput(l, prod(i = 1, n, x[i])), 1); listsort(l, 1); #l \\ _David A. Corneth_, Jan 02 2019
